<HL>
   Magna International
   Plans to Issue Shares
   And Pay Down Debt
</HL>
<DATE>
10/31/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   MAGAF TMG.A
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
AUTO PARTS AND EQUIPMENT INCLUDING TIRES (AUP)
